\begin_layout Section
Installation
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The first thing to do is to uncompress the zip file into some folder.
 Use your preferred application for this, usually doing click or double
 click over it will start the application that will allow you to uncompress
 it.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Once uncompressed you will get a folder like 
\emph on
gitools-1.5.0-bin
\emph default
 (the version number could be different depending on which version you downloade
d).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
That's all, you have already installed Gitools in your computer if you only
 want to work with the graphical interface.
\end_layout

